For everyone's edification:

If you actually need topographical maps of Norway, this is probably the set you want.  This is a 20 CD set.  Each CD is fairly small; the average is roughly 35MB.  The 20 CD's together cover all of Norway.

There is a 21st CD, the 1:250000 (aka low resolution) overview map set.  Very useful for a quick glance.

These maps don't require any codes.  The maps aren't routable - they're topo maps, afterall, not driving maps.  They do, however, have roads, cities and so on.
